Let's take our minds off this Global Thermonuclear War business, and lets play
som Tic-Tac-Toe! Make a Tic-Tac-Toe playing AI and have it either play games
against you or against itself.

If it plays against you, it should always win or draw, regardless of who goes
first. If it plays against itself, it should always draw.

Here's how the beginning of a game might look in a terminal window (this is
just a suggestion, yours can look however you want it to look, you could even
make a GUI if you really wanted to):
